text: Barnumton is an unincorporated community in Camden County, in the U.S. state of Missouri. ==History== A post office called Barnumton was established in 1867, and remained in operation until 1956. The community's name honors a Barnum family of settlers. ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in Camden County, Missouri Category:Unincorporated communities in Missouri
title: Barnumton, Missouri
